{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20",
    "translationId": "brenton",
    "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 20,
    "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20",
    "summary": "Source text for 2 Chronicles 20 in Brenton Septuagint."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.1",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:1",
      "text": "And in regard to all these circumstances we make a covenant, and write it, and our princes, our Levites, and our priests, set their seal to it.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.2",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:2",
      "text": "And over them that sealed were Neemias the Artasastha, son of Achalia, and Zedekias,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.3",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:3",
      "text": "the son of Aræa, and Azaria, and Jeremia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.4",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:4",
      "text": "Phasur, Amaria, Melchia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.5",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:5",
      "text": "Attus, Sebani, Maluch,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.6",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:6",
      "text": "Iram, Meramoth, Abdia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.7",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:7",
      "text": "Daniel, Gannathon, Baruch,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.8",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:8",
      "text": "Mesulam, Abia, Miamin,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.9",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:9",
      "text": "Maazia, Belgai, Samaia; these were priests.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.10",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:10",
      "text": "And the Levites; Jesus the son of Azania, Banaiu of the sons of Enadad, Cadmiel",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.11",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:11",
      "text": "and his brethren, Sabania, Oduia, Calitan, Phelia, Anan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.12",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:12",
      "text": "Micha, Roob, Asebias,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.13",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:13",
      "text": "Zacchor, Sarabia, Sebania,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.14",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:14",
      "text": "Odum, the sons of Banuæ.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.15",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:15",
      "text": "The heads of the people; Phoros, Phaath Moab, Elam, Zathuia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.16",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:16",
      "text": "the sons of Bani, Asgad, Bebai,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.17",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:17",
      "text": "Adania, Bagoi, Hedin,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.18",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:18",
      "text": "Ater, Ezekia, Azur,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.19",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:19",
      "text": "Oduia, Esam, Besi,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.20",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:20",
      "text": "Ariph, Anathoth, Nobai,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.21",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:21",
      "text": "Megaphes, Mesullam, Ezir,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.22",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:22",
      "text": "Mesozebel, Saduc, Jeddua,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.23",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:23",
      "text": "Phaltia, Anan, Anæa,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.24",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:24",
      "text": "Osee, Anania, Asub,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.25",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:25",
      "text": "Aloes, Phalaï, Sobec,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.26",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:26",
      "text": "Reum, Essabana, Maasia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.27",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:27",
      "text": "and Aia, Ænan, Enam,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.28",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:28",
      "text": "Maluch, Eram, Baana.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.29",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:29",
      "text": "And the rest of the people, the priests, the Levites, the porters, the singers, the Nathinim, and every one who drew off from the nations of the land to the law of God, their wives, their sons, their daughters, every one who had knowledge and understanding,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.30",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:30",
      "text": "were urgent with their brethren, and bound them under a curse, and entered into a curse, and into an oath, to walk in the law of God, which was given by the hand of Moses, the servant of God; to keep and to do all the commandments of the Lord, and his judgments, and his ordinances;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.31",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:31",
      "text": "and that we will not, they said, give our daughters to the people of the land, nor will we take their daughters to our sons.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.32",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:32",
      "text": "And as for the people of the land who bring wares and all manner of merchandise to sell on the sabbath-day, we will not buy of them on the sabbath or on the holy day: and we will leave the seventh year, and the exaction of every debt.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.33",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:33",
      "text": "And we will impose ordinances upon ourselves, to levy on ourselves the third part of a didrachm yearly for the service of the house of our God;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.34",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:34",
      "text": "the shewbread, and the continual meat-offering, and for the continual wholeburnt-offering, of the sabbaths, of the new moon, for the feasts, and for the holy things, and the sin-offerings, to make atonement for Israel, and for the works of the house of our God.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.35",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:35",
      "text": "And we cast lots for the office of wood-bearing, we the priests, and the Levites, and the people, to bring wood into the house of our God, according to the house of our families, at certain set times, year by year, to burn on the altar of the Lord our God, as it is written in the law:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.36",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:36",
      "text": "and to bring the first-fruits of our land, and the first-fruits of the fruit of every tree, year by year, into the house of the Lord:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.37",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:37",
      "text": "the first-born of our sons, and of our cattle, as it is written in the law, and the first-born of our herds and of our flocks, to bring to the house of our God, for the priests that minister in the house of our God.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.38",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:38",
      "text": "And the first-fruits of our corn, and the fruit of every tree, of wine, and of oil, will we bring to the priests to the treasury of the house of God; and a tithe of our land to the Levites: for the Levites themselves shall receive tithes in all the cities of the land we cultivate.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.39",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:39",
      "text": "And the priest the son of Aaron shall be with the Levites in the tithe of the Levite: and the Levites shall bring up the tenth part of their tithe to the house of our God, into the treasuries of the house of God.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "brenton:second-chronicles.20.40",
      "translationId": "brenton",
      "bookSlug": "second-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 20,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "2 Chronicles 20:40",
      "text": "For the children of Israel and the children of Levi shall bring into the treasuries the first-fruits of the corn, and wine, and oil; and there are the holy vessels, and the priests, and the ministers, and the porters, and the singers: and we will not forsake the house of our God.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
